text:
The issue is HubSpot database is updated on the form submit, and then your page redirects before the update happens.

The best workaround for this is to modify the code of the form submission to submit, then timeout for a second or two before redirecting to the landing page.

The next best workaround is sending it to some temporary “Gate” Page that has a loading module on it, then

```&lt;div class="loading-icon"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
setTimeout(() =&gt; {
  window.location.href = '<https://newpage.com/typ>"
}, 3500)
&lt;/script&gt;```
